
<% if @resource.sign_in_count > 1 %>
Hello <%= @resource.unconfirmed_email %>,

________________________________________


New Email Address For BulldogClip Account

________________________________________


We have received a request to change your BulldogClip account email address 
from <%= @resource.email %> to <%= @resource.unconfirmed_email %>. To confirm
